# WordGuessGame - A Classic Word Guessing Experience 🎮📖

Welcome to the **WordGuessGame** repository! This is a Java-based implementation of the classic word guessing game, inspired by Hangman and Wordle.

## Game Objective 🎯
Guess a randomly selected word one letter at a time before running out of attempts.

## Key Features ✨
- Dynamic word selection from customizable word lists
- Interactive gameplay with masked word display
- Input validation and guess tracking
- Win/loss conditions with feedback
- Optional features: Hangman visualization, hint system, replayability

## Technical Implementation 💻
- Main class: `WordGuessGame.java`
- Core functionalities: word selection, input validation, progress tracking
- Uses Java Standard Libraries (Random, Scanner, File I/O)

## Quick Start 🚀
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Eshan-Mishra/WordGuessGame.git
javac WordGuessGame.java
java WordGuessGame
```

